headline.print_headline: Study Looks at Mortality in Post-Soviet Era
headline.main: Study Looks at Mortality in Post-Soviet Era

docs.lead_paragraph: Rapid privatization in several former Soviet states and satellites in the early 1990s contributed to rising mortality rates, according to a new study.
